      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/czechs-cut-rates-as-trump-win-adds-to-risks-to-growth-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济增长疲软掩盖了通胀风险的担忧，捷克决策者连续第八次降息。]]></description>
